hero.title: Docgeni
hero.description: Out of the box Angular Component Document Generator

features.title: Out of the box
features.description: Automatically generate navigation and menus according to the directory structure, and help developers get started at zero cost through command-line tools, so that you can quickly start  writing document and development component

features.title: Born for Angular Component Development
features.description: Independent angular component preview experience that contains component overview, examples, APIs and rich markdown extensions make it easier to write documents and support multiple libraries at one site

features.title: Two modes and multiple styles support
features.description: Full and Lite modes are supported to meet different needs. At the same time, default and angular styles are supported to allow users to choose their own themes

features.title: Powerful Customization
features.description: It provides publicDir to realize features such as custom HTML, resources and styles, and supports AppModule metadata and fully customized site

features.title: Automatic Generation of Component API
features.description: Automatically generate component APIs based on typescript type definitions and comments, and maintain the consistency of code and documents
